                <a class="anchor" id="top" name="AGM"></a><h3>Sanderstead Residents' Association AGM Wednesday 20th May at 7.30 pm</h3>
                <p>The Sanderstead Residents' Association AGM will be held on Wednesday 20th May at 7.30 pm in All Saints Church Hall, Onslow Gardens, Sanderstead, CR2 9AB. All members are enttiled to vote at the meeting.
                </p>
