                <a class="anchor" id="top" name="railway"></a><h3>Model Railway Show. Saturday 13 June 2020</h3>
                <p>Saturday 13 June at St Paul's URC, Croham Park Avenue CR2 7HF, from 10.00 am until 4.00 pm. Supported by Croydon Model Railway Society with 10 or more layouts in gauges N, 00, and 009. There will also be trade stands, demonstrations and a secondhand/pre-owned stall. Admission is Adults (£5), Children under 16 (£3), and Families - 2 + 2 (£12). Refreshments, including hot and cold snacks and meals, will be available all day. Details 01883 723081.</p>
                <p>This is the second South Croydon Model Railway Show.</p>
